column4: I am a student and an Emerging Media Artist at Nebraska Public Media
column6: I am a student at the Johnny Carson Center for Emerging Media Arts and Im studying to be a VFX artist. I have been working in the Adobe CreativeSuite, DaVinci Resolve, and Maya Autodesk for over 10 years now. I am a 3D modeling artist, an editor, photographer, videographer, VFX artist, and digital media artist. I do a lot of digital motion graphics as well, and i use AI for inspiration for a lot of projects especially since the new updates to Adobe this year. After the Adobe Max conference this year, i look forward to more of whats coming from them in terms of AI, especially since its already becoming difficult to tell the difference between AI generagted art and art from humans.
